## Linxira Skills

Project-local Linxira content is materialized as a progressive routing tree under
`.agents/skills/`. Read only one matching top-level router first:

{{routes}}

Follow that router to one second-level index, then load only the exact leaf skill
required by the task. Do not scan or preload the complete tree. Follow the
selected leaf's risk and completion requirements before action.
<!-- linxira-skills:end -->
